AD_TABLE.NAME: Efin_BudgetAdjline
AD_TABLE.HELP: Table used to hold details of original budget Adjustment Details

AD_TABLE.NAME: Efin_Budget_Actual
AD_TABLE.DESCRIPTION: Actual tab under budget inquiry line

AD_TABLE.NAME: Efin_Apply_Prepayment
AD_TABLE.HQLQUERY: select @selectClause@ from Invoice as inv join inv.efinManualencumbrance as enc join inv.documentType as type with type.efinIsprepayinv='Y' left join inv.efinAppliedPrepaymentEfinAppliedInvoiceList as api where @additional_filters@ and @whereClause@ group by inv.id having coalesce(inv.grandTotalAmount,0) >coalesce(sum(api.appliedAmount),0)

AD_TABLE.NAME: Efin_Budgetadj
AD_TABLE.HELP: Table used to hold details original budget Adjustment Details

AD_TABLE.NAME: Efin_budgethistory
AD_TABLE.HQLQUERY: select @selectClause@ from Efin_budgethistory_V his where @additional_filters@ and @whereClause@ group by @groupByClause@ @havingClause@

AD_TABLE.NAME: Efin_Budgrev_Inquiry_V
AD_TABLE.HQLQUERY: select @selectClause@ from Efin_Budget_Transfertrxline as revln left join revln.efinBudgetTransfertrx as rev where @additional_filters@ and @whereClause@ group by @groupByClause@ @havingClause@

AD_TABLE.NAME: Efin_Account_Budget_Inquiry
AD_TABLE.HQLQUERY: Select tr.id as Id,tr.transfertype as TransferType,tr.revisionno as RevisionNo,tr.period as Period, (select max(to_date(substr(hijri_date, 7,2)||'-'||substr(hijri_date, 5,2)||'-'||substr(hijri_date, 1,4),'DD-MM-YYYY')) from EUT_HijiriDates where gregorianDate = TO_DATE( to_char(tr.accountdate,'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD') ) as AccountDate, (select max( to_date(substr(hijri_date, 7,2)||'-'||substr(hijri_date, 5,2)||'-'||substr(hijri_date, 1,4),'DD-MM-YYYY') )from EUT_HijiriDates where gregorianDate = TO_DATE( to_char(tr.transferdate,'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD') ) as TransferDate, (select max(to_date(substr(hijri_date, 7,2)||'-'||substr(hijri_date, 5,2)||'-'||substr(hijri_date, 1,4),'DD-MM-YYYY')) from EUT_HijiriDates where gregorianDate = TO_DATE( to_char(tr.creationDate,'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD') ) as creationDate, (select max( to_date(substr(hijri_date, 7,2)||'-'||substr(hijri_date, 5,2)||'-'||substr(hijri_date, 1,4),'DD-MM-YYYY') )from EUT_HijiriDates where gregorianDate = TO_DATE( to_char(tr.updated,'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD') ) as updated, tr.dr as Dr,tr.cr as Cr,tr.net as Net, tr.description as Description from Efin_Acc_Budget_Inquiry_V tr where 1=1 and @additional_filters@ and @whereClause@
